{"tid":1596813,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《緊急》好似好耐冇set deadline 俾仆街港共","createTime":"2019-09-26T16:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T19:05:58.000Z","uid":262346,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96e37a7004a2cb77bba01e22be99bae6cd738a49","tid":1596813,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:09:16.000Z","msg":"之前行動成功係因為港共冇回應訴求<br />\n行動就有條件升級<br />\n<br />\n最近黑警同黨鐵太仆街<br />\n所以多左報復性行動<br />\n<br />\n同時又等美國搞個法案<br />\n<br />\n其實唔關事架<br />\n照set deadline 俾港共<br />\n佢唔跪低就升級<br />\n<br />\n唔係有美國人權法案就停哂手架<br />\n<br />\n急需明確deadline去逼呢個仆街政權"},{"pid":"8df23c70ed4eb59cd00b83f14167130c93e37df1","tid":1596813,"uid":262346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭回應實係拖得就拖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人 理撚得你 唔跪低就升級<br />\n<br />\n攞返個主導權"},{"pid":"fc2365c81b24c6894a3a6701d4121e5ea8c9c5ed","tid":1596813,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"498842dd9c4d8aecb49342ff18aac89b427859b0","tid":1596813,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"10月1 讀宣言都有deadline 成份"},{"pid":"2a9878625ae65ff7d2e0f2fb4baaa462c0670986","tid":1596813,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"498842dd9c4d8aecb49342ff18aac89b427859b0","tid":1596813,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"10月1 讀宣言都有deadline 成份"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"10月1搞大佢"},{"pid":"bc1de39aa1e73ea375935628841fb2bff763d0d0","tid":1596813,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a9878625ae65ff7d2e0f2fb4baaa462c0670986","tid":1596813,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"498842dd9c4d8aecb49342ff18aac89b427859b0","tid":1596813,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:13:13.